Tender Announcement
=================
* **Contracting Entity**: Health Canada (Santé Canada)
* **Procurement Title**: TSPS Stream 3.2 Project Manager (Senior) for the Canadian Drug Agency Transition Office
* **Procurement Number**: cb-6244-74963338
* **Procurement Category**: Service (`SRV`)

The Canadian Drug Agency Transition Office was established to provide dedicated capacity and leadership to develop recommendations, an implementation plan and staging to establish a Canadian Drug Agency (CDA). The contracting entity seeks project management expertise to lead project management processes for the CDA project, including liaising with internal and external team members across workstreams to develop, track and update project plans and report on project implementation.
